{"tid":2518191,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人形胖虎只花半年改造成功 現擁美隊身形冀拍第一次拖","createTime":"2021-05-06T00:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-06T02:07:33.000Z","uid":167566,"like":28,"dislike":136,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c91e1d997d6d7f3bd55ee9b16ad0c780af3060","tid":2518191,"uid":167566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmUG6BuCxG9QnSPo3BYKhFJmwUuKoCfubHy93GWnyWheUu?filename=7BoxD9p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7BoxD9p.png&h=9c5d765e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n   YouTuber 雞翼（GE) 感情路上波折重重，年前向當紅直播主deer 求愛不遂，後跟多位女性友人曾傳出緋聞始未能在感情路上開花結果。<br />\n<br />\n   遂鹿慘敗&mdash;&mdash;過千翼粉推波助瀾下失手於長達數年的逐鹿戰，使他身心受創。「你有冇勇氣鍾意一個人鍾意咁耐呀！」及後雞翼用一句話感動聊天室，同時宣布雞鹿戀告一段落。<br />\n<br />\n   自強不息，改變自己，尤如漫畫英雄人物。受盡失敗的雞翼並未有放棄，每天出入健身室，僅花半年成功改變自己，雖沒美國隊長外貌，但擁美國隊長身形，成功用行動證明自己。而他亦只希望能夠好好的談第一次戀愛。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好勵志<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70f1036e5c6e44f514903769a31b66b43910769b","tid":2518191,"uid":84081,"like":82,"dislike":3,"score":79,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:32:04.000Z","msg":"咁都美隊身型？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afcf5c9402d79f76d380135ad8c24fb1e6362ca4","tid":2518191,"uid":211461,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:37:45.000Z","msg":"逐鹿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n證明四肢未發達都可以頭腦好簡單"},{"pid":"27f220571751d289b9611336d492f77c5213d85a","tid":2518191,"uid":60977,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:39:58.000Z","msg":"美隊？<br />\n邊忽美？"},{"pid":"58e55928785d7aa20f451305414a9eeb70831d84","tid":2518191,"uid":177089,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-06T00:40:24.000Z","msg":"美隊 (排骨)"},{"pid